query: SELECT count(*) as "count!" FROM backer_payouts WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::int4) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR backer_id = $4::int4) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR asami_amount = $6::decimal) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR disbursement_id = $8::int4) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR paid = $10::boolean) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR created_at = $12::timestamptz)
